  "title": "Project Manager / Senior Project Manager  ( Construction / Main Con & General Building experience  ) Good Pay +Good Bonus",
  "description": "<p>· Develop and manage project plans, timelines, and budgets to ensure successful project delivery</p>\n<p>· Coordinate and collaborate with cross-functional teams, including architects, engineers, subcontractors, and clients, to ensure seamless project execution</p>\n<p>· Monitor project progress and identify and mitigate potential risks or issues, implementing remedial actions as necessary</p>\n<p>· Manage procurement and logistics, ensuring the timely delivery of materials and equipment to the construction site</p>\n<p>· Ensure compliance with all relevant safety, quality, and environmental regulations</p>\n<p>· Provide regular project updates and reports to senior management and clients</p>\n<p>· Mentor and manage a team of site engineers and project coordinators</p>\n<p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p>\n<p>· Minimum of 5–7 years of experience as a Project Manager in residential construction projects</p>\n<p>· Degree in Civil Engineering, Construction Management, or a related field</p>\n<p>· Strong project management skills, with the ability to plan, coordinate, and execute complex construction projects</p>\n<p>· · <strong>Good Pay + Good allowance + Good Bonus</strong></p>\n<p>· · Interested candidates please send an updated Resume / CV in Ms Word format to<strong> lilian@recruitflash.com</strong> or WhatsApp’s your resume to <strong>98332779 ( no Calls)</strong></p>\n<p>· · <strong>Consultant in-charge : Quah Li Lian (Lilian) ( Registration No: R1983286 )</strong></p>",
